<div id="02" class="popup_block">
<div id="text">
 
<img src="https://static.tumblr.com/j0nrc4i/p84p4uxt0/rules.png" draggable="false"></p>
 
<h2>Pages.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> <b>Please</b> read my pages before asking me any questions. If you can’t access them for any reason, just let me know. There’s a lot of valuable information, such as what verse’s I currently have and vital information on my muse.</p>
 
<h2>Following & Selectivity.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> This blog is Semi-Selective. Meaning–I will follow most people back. The only time I will not follow back is if I do not forsee us interacting. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> I will likely not respond to character on character interaction if we are not mutuals.</p>
 
<h2>To Personal Blogs.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> Unfortunately, I do not follow most personal blogs back, except maybe for close friends. It’s just to keep my dashboard tidy, and it’s nothing against you personally. You’re still welcome to message me and send asks, regardless.
 
<h2>Content.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> This blog is likely to have triggering content & darker themes. Most things will be tagged appropriately, but if that is not your cup of tea, <b>please do not follow me</b>. It is my blog, and I can rp what I wish.</p>
 
 
<h2>Icons & Graphics.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> <b>DO NOT</b> steal any icons or graphics from this page<i>!</i> If they aren’t made by me, they are made by friends or other people. If you wish to use anything, please ask me first.</br>
Icon borders courtesy of <b><a href="https://vestigeofcalamity.tumblr.com/">vestigeofcalamity</a></b>.</p>
 
<a name="sect5"><h2>Replies and Asks.</h2></a><p>
 
<b>✿</b> Reminding me about replies is fine, but please try not to pester me<i>!</i> I’m a law student, so I may not always have the time or muse to reply right away. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> On this note–rp activity will be sporadic throughout the work week. While I may lurk and reblog things, maybe even reply to one liners, actual rping will be very sporadic. I’m not ignoring our threads, I promise. During the weekend I will answer all asks and reply to threads.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> Reply length. There’s no need to match my reply length, but I do require my partners to put in similar effort. If I write multiple paragraphs and I receive a one liner in return, it seems like they don’t care enough. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> if you’ve lost muse for a thread and wish to drop it, just message me. I won’t bite your head off. In the same respect, I will message you if I no longer wish to continue a thread. </p>
 
<h2>Multiple Threads.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> Even if we have an ongoing thread, don’t hesitate to send in more asks or tag me in starters. We’ll either finish 5000 threads, drop them all, or do whatever we want. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> i.e. I welcome multiple threads, let’s do the thing.</p>
 
<h2>Thread List.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> I have a list of all ongoing threads under the RP Tracker listed on my navigation page. Please feel free to reference this at any time to see if I have your reply or have responded. I will be updating this periodically, so if I am missing a thread please inform me.
 
<h2>Interactions.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> If we are mutuals, do the thing. Tag me in starters, send ask memes, do whatever. I may still respond if we are not mutuals, but I reserve the right to not.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> You have express permission to do whatever you want to my muse, including <b>darker content</b>. However, keep in mind my muse will not go down quietly. Expect realistic reactions to whatever you do. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> Muse does not equal Mun. If my muse does not like yours, don’t take it personally. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> <b>FEEL FREE</b> <b>(</b> <i>plz do</i> <b>)</b> add other characters into our threads. Family, random merchant, other muses, I don’t care. Make it feel real, we’re telling a story. Stories tend to have more than two characters involved.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> This blog is multiverse. Each verse will have a separate tag. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> If there is not a verse for your fandom, and none of the existing ones work for you <b>(</b> <i>or you just want to</i> <b>)</b>, feel free to message me about it! I love creating new verses.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> Feel free to mention my muse to other muses if we’ve interacted! I love things like that.
 
<h2>Anonymous Asks.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> Send them<i>!</i> Do as you wish, send whatever you like, unless I specifically request otherwise in these rules.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> Reference current rp events if you want<i>!</i> Ask questions, be the narrator to set up a situation for me. I love anons.
 
<h2>Posts.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> I’m okay with seeing ooc posts, but the mun doesn’t like to see too many political posts. I understand that some people may feel strongly about a certain subject, but I would rather not see it. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> Please tag your things appropriately and we won’t have many issues.
 
<h2>NSFW.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> Although I’m 18+, I don’t feel comfortable doing smut with just anyone. This doesn’t mean I won’t do it, just shoot me a message first to make sure I’m okay with it.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> Mun will <b>not</b> rp smut with those under the age of 18.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> Do <b>NOT</b> send me explicit asks <b>(</b> <i>sexual in nature</i> <b>)</b> on anonymous. It is simply creepy. Cute romantic stuff is okay, but sexual asks are a big <b>no</b> unless I have a face to look at.
 
<h2>Relationships.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> This blog's Main Ship is with <b><a href="https://vestigeofcalamity.tumblr.com/">vestigeofcalamity</a></b>. All interactions within the <b>Noragami</b> verse are set with this status by default. However, I am not ship <b>exclusive</b> with vestigeofcalamity. If you want to ship or otherwise have our interactions set in an altered verse, then simply message me! </p>
 
<b>✿</b> I ship CHEMISTRY. Some ships will likely come easier than others. If you are interested in shipping with my muse, please let me know. Otherwise, I want the development to be as natural as possible. If it’s there, it’s there. </p>
 
<b>✿</b> Same note–one sided feelings are completely okay. Your muse is entirely welcome to have their own feelings about mine, but my muse is not obligated to return them. Please keep this in mind.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> This blog is multiship. I will consider single ship for each particular verse if my partner expresses interest in this. However, I cannot be exclusive as a whole, due to the nature of this blog as multi-verse. Please consult me if you are interested in this.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> Polymarous relationships are <b>not</b> off limits, but if you’re interested in something like that, you will have to convince my muse in character.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> Pre-established relationships are A-OK, just consult me beforehand. </p>
 
<h2>Tagging.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> ;unrelated for anything that may not be related to my blog.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> tw;trigger for any triggers<i>!</i> If I am not tagging a trigger of yours, please let me know<i>!</i></p>
 
<b>✿</b> ;the writer has something to say | ooc ✿ for any out of character posts</p>
 
<b>✿</b> ;psa for any important info.</p>
 
<b>✿</b> I also have various tags for any characters I may like or interact with, so just look around for those.
 
<h2>Social.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> Discord or Line is available for mutuals upon request.
 
<h2>Have fun.</h2>
 
<b>✿</b> The most important rule, make sure to have fun! Roleplaying is supposed to be fun, not something you dread. Just relax and enjoy yourself.
 
</div>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
 
<div id="03" class="popup_block">
<div id="text">
<img src="https://static.tumblr.com/j0nrc4i/uHFp4uxl4/about.png" draggable="false"></p>
 
<h2>Profile.</h2></a>
 
<b>Name:</b> Tо̄ Miya (杜 美夜)</br>
 
<b>VA:</b> <a href="https://youtu.be/CsZCOT_eqdA?t=40">Nana Mizuki</a></br>
 
<b>Nickname:</b> Christine; Chris; Mi-chan</br>
 
<b>Hair Color: </b>Pink</br>
 
<b>Eye Color:</b> Cyan</br>

<b>Species:</b> Human? (Half-Human/Half-<a href="https://eraba-reta-unmei.tumblr.com/tagged/%3Babout%20the%20spirits">Spirit</a>)</p>

<b>Ethnicity:</b> Asian <b>(</b> <i>Chinese</i> <b>)</b>; European <b>(</b> <i>Greek</i> <b>)</b></br>
 
<b>Age:</b> Varies; 16-22 </br>
 
<b>Height:</b> 5’7</br>
 
<b>Sexuality:</b> Heterosexual, Demiromantic</br>
 
<b>Birth date:</b> April 12th [Aries]</br>
 
<h2>Personality.</h2>
 
There are many words to describe her. You might call her compassionate and courageous; others may call her gullible and reckless. <b>Violent</b>--certainly at times. Far from perfect, easy to fluster, and yes, a social awkwardness that often makes simple conversation more challenging than it ought to be. </p>

Then there's her tendency to push people away; it's hard to miss. One might stop and marvel at her hypocritical behavior. A yearning for social involvement, and yet a spit-fire personality that's hard to handle. An extraordinary habit of finding trouble where no trouble should be. Yet, she still prefers the ordinary and peaceful lifestyle. Whatever the case, it is evident that there is at least some guiding principle to her spontaneous and confusing behavior: <i>do what is right, and do what you must.</i></p>
 
**Note: For related background info, please reference the verse page.</p>

***Note: The spirits referenced on this blog are of my own creation. Information can be found <a href="https://eraba-reta-unmei.tumblr.com/tagged/%3Babout%20the%20spirits">here</a> and <a href="https://maledictus-maleficus.tumblr.com/tagged/%3Babout%20the%20spirits">here</a>.
 
</div>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
 
<div id="04" class="popup_block">
<div id="text">
 
<img src="https://static.tumblr.com/j0nrc4i/Nbjp4uy2b/verses.png"></p>
 
<ul id="tabs">
<li class="active">General.</li>
<li>Modern.</li>
<li>Crossover</li>
</ul>
<ul id="tab">
<li class="active">
 
<i>These verses are used for general purposes when no specific verse is available.</i>
 
<div class="links_list">
<p class="links_head">Modern Verse.</p>
<div class="links_body">
 
<b>tagged:</b> <a href="/tagged/verse;modern">verse;modern</a></p>
 
This verse is set during modern times. In this verse, Miya is either a senior in high school, a college student, or a detective that also takes on freelance work on occasion. In all verses, she lives on her own. </p>
 
</div></div>
 
<div class="links_list">
<p class="links_head">Urban Fantasy Verse.</p>
<div class="links_body">
 
<b>tagged:</b> <a href="/tagged/verse;urban%20fantasy">verse;urban fantasy</a></p>
 
In this verse, her abilities are nearly identical to that of her Fate verse (please see the information on this verse for a list of abilities.) She has knowledge of the supernatural world and of magic. Any verse set in modern times but also has a fantasy twist to it will be set this in this verse by default unless requested otherwise.
 
Just like her modern verse, in this verse she will be either a high school student, a college student, or a detective who accepts freelance work. If she is a detective, she primarily handles supernatural cases.
</p>
 
<h2>Background.</h2>
 
<b>(</b> <i>under construction</i> <b>)</b></p>
 
<h2>Abilities.</h2>
 
<b>Sixth Sense</b> - In this verse, she has a broad understanding of magic and the supernatural. As such, she has a sixth sense. This allows her to both see and feel things normal humans usually cannot perceive. This power mostly stems from her interaction with the supernatural and her magic.</p>
 
<b>Empath</b></p>
 
Miya has the ability to tune in to the emotions of those around her,  even to the point of feeling them herself.  Often she does this unconsciously without thinking about it,  but she can choose to “zone in”  on someone particular. </p>
 
The ability isn’t absolute and Miya often has a hard time “reading”  certain people until they’ve opened up to her a little. </p>
 
 
<b>Spirit Magic.</b></p>
To call Miya a 'magus' would not be innacurate but neither is it entirely accurate. Miya practices an art that has fallen largely out of practice, Spirit Magic.  Spirit Magic consists of two steps: <b>communion</b> and <b>manipulation.</b> This type of magic relies on communing with the spirits, asking for their aid, and then directing their powers via manipulation.  </p>
 
Currently she has a connection to the spirits of fire, water, and wind. </p>
 
<b>Child of the Spirits.</b></p>
 
Miya has been blessed since birth with the innate ability to communicate with the elemental spirits around her as if she were talking to another human.  To do so is second nature to her as simple as walking. </p>
 
<b>Fire Mana Manipulation.</b></p>
 
Fire mana.  The source of life.  It what brings warmth to the world,  filling space with heat that can both caress and scorch.  The primary source?  The sun.  </p>
 
Manipulating fire mana is to ask the fire spirits for aid.  The fire spirits are dense concentrations of mana,  discernible to only those that have been blessed by fire in some way.
By manipulating fire mana you can cause the air to combust,  temperatures to raise,  even melt steel if given enough time and pressure.  But also,  it means the ability to take away fire mana;  to freeze water molecules in the air as the mana leaves the atmosphere.  It's as simple as asking the fire spirits to leave for awhile. </p>
 
<b>Fire Mana Affinity </b></p>
 
Miya was born with a unusually high affinity for fire mana manipulation.  The core of her own mana is unusually concentrated with fire mana,  leaving it difficult to control other attributes.  The has left her with the ability see fire spirits and commune with them,  often asking them for their aid.
Unconsciously,  she pulls fire mana in from her surroundings when she has exhausted part of her reservoir.  Maybe the fire spirits themselves are just trying to help.  However, this can have a negative effect on her body in the long run if it exceeds her body’s ability to handle the stress.  It can begin with skin flaking,  then her complexion turning pale.  Eventually,  her body will break down completely and organs will cease to function.</p>
 
<b>High Mana Capacity</b></p>
 
Miya has a high capacity to house mana within her spiritual core.  More than the average human.  Typically,  a human body can only house so much mana before it begins to overflow and break down the body.  Miya’s storage capacity is higher,  meaning her body can handle more stress before breaking down. </p>
 
</p>
 
</div></div>
 
</li>
<li>
 
<i>These verses all take part in an ordinary, modern setting.</i>
 
<div class="links_list">
<p class="links_head">Yakuza verse.</p>
<div class="links_body">
 
<b>tagged:</b> <a href="/tagged/verse;yakuza">verse;yakuza</a></p>
 
This verse is also set during modern times, but is in Japan. Once again, she lives in a large city and is a third year in high school. However, this verse is very specific and cannot be changed at will. In this verse, she lives alone and supports herself, but her father is still very much involved in her life. Her father is a high ranking Yakuza, although she did not know of this until very recently. Despite her father being a Yakuza, she is neither for or against either side. <b>(</b> <i>Yakuza vs. Police</i> <b>)</b></p>
 
</div></div>
 
</li>
<li>
 
Specfic verses associated with fandoms. Reserved for interaction with characters from each fandom. Each crossover verse will have <i>mains</i> in order to preserve continuity. If you're interested in becoming a main shoot me a DM!
 
