                <b>Delusions verse:</b> Chris is 26 and working as a lawyer for a large law firm in the city. She is currently engaged to ancientcalamity’s Yato. <i><a href="/tagged/verse;delusions">verse;delusions</a></i></p>
 
                <b>No Escape:</b> This verse makes use of ancientcalamity’s Yandere verse.  She is currently 19, and the object of his obsession. They are officially “together” at this time. <i><a href="/tagged/verse;no-escape">verse;no escape</a></i></p>
 
