</p>
 
<div class="links_list">
<p class="links_head">Ozymandias.</p>
<div class="links_body">
 
<a href="https://ardenssolis.tumblr.com"><img src="https://66.media.tumblr.com/ce043a7ea963d657ac45d83b1678e95f/6009186a9ecede85-1c/s100x200/37daed69cd6b3b3749a487227f3a63330b777f22.png" align="right" style="height:85px;width:85px;padding-right:5px;padding-bottom:0px;"></a>
</p>
 
[Bully/Local Man with a God Complex/Definitely NOT Attractive]<br>
Miya and Ozymandias have one problem: they are both way too alike.  They're both stubborn and prideful to a fault.  Worst of all, Ozymandias is a total bully towards her!  How dare he say she'd be a terrible wife.<br><br>
 
Despite this, Miya doesn't hate him.  She holds affection towards him and his stubborn ways, but good luck getting her to ever admit to it.  She <i>still</i> thinks he's an egotistical jerk.<br><br>
 
Bond Level: ✿✿✿✿✿
 
 

</div></div> </p>
 
 
</li>
<li>
 
<div class="links_list">
<p class="links_head">Lucky.</p>
<div class="links_body">
 
<a href="https://rakkirrrowch.tumblr.com"><img src="https://66.media.tumblr.com/b4ee2519d716a1c468c319436cf335e9/749d179b6d05c7d1-75/s540x810/7a1318100eb2149a7b40f7ed533834167e45cd3d.png" align="right" style="height:85px;width:85px;padding-right:5px;padding-bottom:0px;"></a>
</p>
 
[Boyfriend/Local Accident Waiting to Happen]<br>
Lucky walked into her life one day and now she can't imagine living without him. Hyperactive and loving, Lucky gave Miya the one thing she had been missing out on in life: someone who cares.  Platonic love became something more romantic, and then one day in spring they decided to officially get together.<br><br>
 
Miya doesn't understand him all the time, and at times his affection can be overbearing.  She worries about him constantly due to his inclination towards accidents, but he has become someone truly irreplacable in her life all the same. She couldn't imagine anyone else she'd rather spend her life with.<br><br>
 
Bond Level: ✿✿✿✿✿✿✿✿
 
</div></div> </p>
 
</li>
<li>
 
<div class="links_list">
<p class="links_head">Salem.</p>
<div class="links_body">
 
<a href="https://salemshooter.tumblr.com"><img src="https://66.media.tumblr.com/8a1bff8bf8692a50cab3542eb623c726/212cc2a131092be0-23/s540x810/583f9407bf1be754fc3b3875da2bc99555a2608b.png" align="right" style="height:85px;width:85px;padding-right:5px;padding-bottom:0px;"></a>
</p>
 
[Partner/Local Menace]<br>
Salem was the first digimon Miya chose to be her partner.  And consequently, the <i>only</i> partner.  Sometimes Miya can't get a good read on him.  He pretends to not care but gets jealous at the slightest sign of her showing affection to another.  Despite this, Miya cares for the little imp like she would some delinquent child of hers.  She'll always be there for him, even if he eats all her food. <br><br>
 
Bond Level: ✿✿✿✿✿✿
 
</div></div> </p>
 

